body_html:
I wasn't aware there was a form. Is that for the Google CLA? If that's signed, you should be able to just write the code and send us the PR. Then someone on the team should hopefully review it in a day or so.

Please note you can't push to tensorflow/tensorflow. Typically people click the fork button, push to their personal repo, and then use that to create the PR.

body:
I wasn't aware there was a form. Is that for the Google CLA? If that's signed, you should be able to just write the code and send us the PR. Then someone on the team should hopefully review it in a day or so.

Please note you can't push to tensorflow/tensorflow. Typically people click the fork button, push to their personal repo, and then use that to create the PR.
